creator: MenuDelite
descriptionHtml:
MenuDelite Management is a dashboard built for MenuDelite business partners to manage their orders and waiter requests in real time and allow their kitchen and waiter staff to effectively meet the needs of their customers.

Set up in seconds, simply download the app, login with your credentials and manage your orders and waiter requests in real time.

View all the order details, including the contents of each order, as well as the payment status, tip, discounts, MenuDelite Credit, and custom dietary requests.

Mark orders as completed once they are fulfilled, and initiate refunds for canceled orders.

View all waiter requests in real time as they arrive and dismiss them with ease once they are addressed.

Spend more time growing your business and let us handle all the heavy lifting.

Get started now!
